  "detailed_description": "<h1>NYAN NYAN PLAZA UPDATE</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/ad232e93f4de4c6737a7e5faac2fbe2d.avif?t=1773812216\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras_big/ad232e93f4de4c6737a7e5faac2fbe2d.avif?t=1773812216 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cats are playing at Nyan Nyan Plaza - a neon-filled retro arcade featuring gachapon machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 40 new levels to solve in this new arcade-themed world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Cat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stuffie joins the cast as Nekograms' first soft-toy cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Accessories</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye out for three new accessories: Gachapon ball, Game heart (pixel-art style), Claw machine hat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Music</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle along with a new arcade-inspired music track.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/21fe5f605f1b019bf299435d3d49a642.avif?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help cats get to sleep in this adorable game, with novel mechanics based on nonograms and sliding puzzles. Nekograms is easy to learn but does get challenging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/aa20dfe13966a93df44040b6ce7632fd.webp?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats only sleep on cushions. Complete a level by helping all cats get to sleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/b7cd1d1b04d959a80f9a9f0df5dde084.poster.avif?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/b7cd1d1b04d959a80f9a9f0df5dde084.webm?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/b7cd1d1b04d959a80f9a9f0df5dde084.mp4?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/5b148442477651f49682b6a6806bf8d4.webp?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn stars by completing levels in the fewest number of moves. Achieve 3 stars in every level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/55e27e0b1822c7b015de07909e231e35.poster.avif?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/55e27e0b1822c7b015de07909e231e35.webm?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/55e27e0b1822c7b015de07909e231e35.mp4?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/99ae1b4973bc140c4bad788aaba59b9c.webp?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the game to unlock Endless Mode and ascend through different states of cat consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/566edbc642e8e399cf28b4ae94f1416b.poster.avif?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/566edbc642e8e399cf28b4ae94f1416b.webm?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/566edbc642e8e399cf28b4ae94f1416b.mp4?t=1773812216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/e69e4acd62a86c04a7c3d31f5cd15442.webp?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original puzzle mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >160 levels over 4 unique worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 15 different cat breeds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478120/extras/6342ffc22b0a1dd1439afccb6ce083cc.avif?t=1773812216\" width=616 height=171 /></span></p>",
